de.hsos.ecs.richwps.wpsmonitor.boundary.gui.datasource

Interface DataSource

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SemanticProxyData

    public interface DataSource
    A DataSource instance is created by a DataSourceCreator. A DataSource is linked to a resource, like a database or file which contains informations over WPS and WPS-Processes. The DataSource need to know how the specific resource is readed. WpsDescription-Instances should contains a set of WpsProcessDescription-Instances.
    Author:
    Florian Vogelpohl
